Title: Automation Hooks Alignment

Scope: Align AI workflow with project automation (formatting, lint fixes, validations).

Expectations:
- After each TS/TSX edit: run Prettier and ESLint --fix (already configured in `.claude/settings.json`).
- Batch validations by feature before summarizing.
- Prefer non-interactive commands and deterministic outputs.

Frontend Commands:
- yarn --cwd volley-app-frontend lint --max-warnings 0
- yarn --cwd volley-app-frontend build

Backend Commands:
- yarn --cwd volley-app-backend lint --max-warnings 0
- yarn --cwd volley-app-backend test
- yarn --cwd volley-app-backend test:cov (when scope sizable)

Notes:
- Do not modify secrets, CI, or environment without explicit user request.
- Keep output concise; include only relevant fenced snippets.

